def is_complete(board: list[list[int]]) -> bool:
    """
    Check if the board (matrix) has been completely filled with non-zero values.

    >>> is_complete([[1]])
    True

    >>> is_complete([[1, 2], [3, 0]])
    False
    """

    return not any(elem == 0 for row in board for elem in row)
